cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper deals with video-based gaze estimation using deep learning models, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper proposes a method for personal calibration, which is related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The use of deep learning models also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of 3D gaze estimation, which could be related to multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR).
